@startuml screen_transition_overview
left to right direction
skinparam BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam RoundCorner 8
skinparam DefaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 12

title ScreenTransitionOverview - ImportAssignmentSystem

[LoginView] as LoginView
[DashboardView] as DashboardView
[OverviewView] as OverviewView
[RequestView] as RequestView
[SiteView] as SiteView
[InventoryView] as InventoryView
[AllocationView] as AllocationView
[OrderView] as OrderView
[ReceivingView] as ReceivingView
[AdminView] as AdminView

LoginView --> DashboardView : login success
DashboardView --> LoginView : logout

DashboardView --> OverviewView : open operations overview
OverviewView --> DashboardView : back to dashboard

DashboardView --> RequestView : UC001 ManageImportRequests
RequestView --> DashboardView : back to dashboard

DashboardView --> SiteView : UC002 ManageSiteInformation
SiteView --> DashboardView : back to dashboard

DashboardView --> InventoryView : UC003 CollectInventoryData
InventoryView --> DashboardView : back to dashboard

DashboardView --> AllocationView : UC004 PlanImportAllocation
AllocationView --> DashboardView : back to dashboard

DashboardView --> OrderView : UC005 PlaceOverseasOrders
OrderView --> DashboardView : back to dashboard

DashboardView --> ReceivingView : UC006 ReceiveAndReconcileGoods
ReceivingView --> DashboardView : back to dashboard

DashboardView --> AdminView : UC007 ManageSystem
AdminView --> DashboardView : back to dashboard

@enduml
